item.dc:creator: @gimpie gimpie
item.description:
@gimpie wrote:

so you added some npc spawn codes, correct? from what it looks like you only added them to npc handler and not to npcspawn or vice versa. add what you added to npchandler and add to npcspawn then compile and run! see if that makes a difference

Hope this helps (i have faced issues like that plenty of times but with a 508 so it might be a bit different)
